---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Season #5 - Pixel Craft - Pixel Series">
    <Navigation/>
	<main class="container justify-content-center text-center space-bottom">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <h1 class="primary-title">Pixel Craft Season #5</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col info text-center">
                <p>Season #5 of Pixel Craft this season we have done some major changes such as using Fabric on the servers backend running the Lithium mod, the Carpet mod, and a few other server side things that are handy. We still have datapack from Vanilla Tweaks and CurseForge, with our own custom datapack thrown in there as well. Shops are getting a bit of a downgrade as were using redstone & the honor system for them this season plus we have a few suprises if you are playing on the server this season.</p>
                <p>We have two optional things for people to use if the want and one required thing. The optional things are a Forge & Fabric clients. The required thing is a Custom Resource Pack that we use for the custom things that we wanted to add to the server. You can get all of these from <a class="external-links" href="https://download.pixilaremedia.com/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/season-5/resource-packs" target="_blank">Resource Packs Here</a> and <a class="external-links" href="https://download.pixilaremedia.com/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/season-5/clients" target="_blank">Clients Here</a>.</p>
                <p><a class="downloads" href="https://cdn.roebuck.dev/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/worlds/season_5_end.zip">Ending Map</a></p>
                <p><a class="downloads" href="https://cdn.roebuck.dev/user/pixilare-media/pixel-craft/worlds/season_5_start.zip">Starting Map</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
	</main>
    <Footer/>
</Layout>

<style>
    .container {
        position: absolute;
        left: 12em;
        top: 0em;
        right: 0em;
        color: white;
        font-size: large;
    }
    .justify-content-center {
        -webkit-box-pack: center!important;
        -ms-flex-pack: center!important;
        justify-content: center!important;
    }
    .text-center {
        text-align: center!important;
    }

    .row {
        display: -webkit-box;
        display: -ms-flexbox;
        display: flex;
        -ms-flex-wrap: wrap;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-right: 15px;
        margin-left: 15px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .col {
        -ms-flex-preferred-size: 0;
        flex-basis: 0;
        -webkit-box-flex: 1;
        -ms-flex-positive: 1;
        flex-grow: 1;
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .info {
        border: 3px;
        border-color: lightslategray;
        border-style: inset;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: large;
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 5px;
        background-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.5);
    }
    .downloads {
        color: lightgreen;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .downloads:hover {
        color: mediumseagreen;
    }
    .external-links {
        color: aqua;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .external-links:hover {
        color: rgb(72, 245, 245);
    }
    .space-bottom {
        padding-bottom: 3em;
    }
    .primary-title {
        border: 3px;
        border-color: lightslategray;
        border-style: groove;
        border-radius: 25px;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.5);
    }
</style>
